{
  "name": "noname",
  "version": "1.9.0",
  "productName": "无名杀",
  "description": "游戏内容来源于项目无名杀（https://github.com/libccy/noname），本Electron应用及功能由我制作",
  "main": "main.js",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "electron .",
    "packageWin64": "electron-packager . 无名杀 --platform=win32 --arch=x64 --out=./ --app-version=1.9.0 --icon=noname.ico --overwrite --ignore=node_modules --electron-version 16.0.2",
    "packageWin32": "electron-packager . 无名杀 --platform=win32 --arch=ia32 --out=./ --app-version=1.9.0 --icon=noname.ico --overwrite --ignore=node_modules --electron-version 16.0.2",
    "packageLinux": "electron-packager . 无名杀 --platform=linux --arch=x64 --out=./ --app-version=1.9.0 --icon=noname.ico --overwrite --ignore=node_modules --electron-version 16.0.2",
	"postinstall": "electron-builder install-app-deps",
	"dist": "electron-builder"
  },
  "build": {
    "productName":"无名杀",
    "appId": "com.shijian.noname", 
    "directories": {
      "output": "build"
    },
	"asar": false,
    "win": {  
      "icon": "./resources/app/noname.ico",
	  "target": [{
	    "target": "nsis",
		"arch": ["x64"]
	  }]
    }
  },
  "nsis": {
    "oneClick": false,
	"perMachine": false,
    "allowElevation": true,
    "allowToChangeInstallationDirectory": true,
    "installerIcon": "./resources/app/noname.ico",
    "uninstallerIcon": "./resources/app/noname.ico",
    "installerHeaderIcon": "./resources/app/noname.ico",
    "createDesktopShortcut": true,
    "createStartMenuShortcut": false,
    "shortcutName": "无名杀",
	"uninstallDisplayName": "无名杀 v1.9",
	"include": "build/installer.nsh",
	"artifactName": "无名杀安装程序v1.38.exe",
	"deleteAppDataOnUninstall": false,
	"language": "zh-CN"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/nonameShijian/noname.git"
  },
  "installerVersion": "1.381",
  "installerUpdateContent": [
    {
      "version": "1.381",
      "updateContent": [
        "撤销上个版本的更新",
        "若你使用的是v1.37的安装包，请更换至v1.381的安装包",
        "注意：v1.381的安装包不兼容windows 7，window 7 用户请尝试v1.36的安装包",
		"内置无名杀全教程V9.9完整版"
      ]
    },
	{
      "version": "1.38",
      "updateContent": [
        "main.js中对部分代码的顺序进行调整，修复某些代码执行太晚而失效的问题",
        "通过【应用配置】扩展修复【制作扩展-选择武将图片】时闪退的问题",
        "修复通过协议更新或下载扩展时remote模块找不到的问题"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.37",
      "updateContent": [
        "修复【应用配置】修改过的alert不会堵塞进程的bug",
        "新增 菜单栏-操作 创建快捷方式",
        "新增 菜单栏-反馈",
        "新增 菜单栏-操作-打开无名杀目录",
        "【应用配置】扩展里可以设置是否修改原生alert和confirm了（变得更美观）",
        "【拖拽读取】扩展v1.75更新",
        "【在线更新】扩展v1.2更新",
        "Electron升级至 V16.0.0 （需要重新安装），支持中文控制台，使用remote模块需要改用require('@electron/remote')"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.36",
      "updateContent": [
        "修复了某些情况下内置扩展丢失的问题（只要不是打开一次游戏前就拿完整包覆盖）",
        "避免第一次进入游戏提示【是否下载图片和字体素材】？（约175MB）",
        "可以通过点击输入框-点击菜单栏-操作-emoji选取或window.showEmojiPanel()唤起emoji选择器"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.35",
      "updateContent": [
        "修复窗口销毁后按esc报错的问题",
        "完善了免费提示",
        "【在线更新】扩展V1.18版本",
        "无名杀全教程V9.8完整版"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.34",
      "updateContent": [
        "修复游戏崩溃后初始界面无限重启的bug"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.33",
      "updateContent": [
        "无名杀全教程9.7完整版"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.32",
      "updateContent": [
        "全屏时隐藏菜单栏（需要用esc退出全屏）"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.31",
      "updateContent": [
        "修复下载扩展的一处代码错误"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.3",
      "updateContent": [
        "可以通过\"菜单栏 -> 操作 -> 检查应用更新\"热更新无名杀本体了",
        "增加\"nonameSkill\"协议",
        "可以通过\"nonameSkill:?extensionName=扩展名\"链接直接下载扩展",
        "新增内置扩展【在线更新】，在扩展界面更新游戏不会崩溃",
        "修复了游戏崩溃后，不显示初始页面而一直反复弹窗的问题",
        "内置无名杀全教程v9.5版本"
      ]
    },
    {
      "version": "1.25",
      "updateContent": [
        "本应用的缓存文件改到应用内resource/app/Home文件夹，请勿删除此文件夹",
        "内置无名杀全教程v9.4版本"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "author": "诗笺",
  "license": "ISC",
  "devDependencies": {
    "electron": "^16.0.2",
    "electron-builder": "^22.14.5",
    "electron-packager": "^15.3.0"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@electron/remote": "^2.0.1"
  }
}
